This a multi-threaded raytracer written in JavaScript with HTML5 features. It's supposed to be run in a browser. See /examples folder with rendered pictures.

Supported browsers:
Chrome 21
Firefox 15
IE 10 (not tested)

Note, that Chrome puts a security restriction that does not allow to run this raytracer from a local disk. To disable this restriction, run Chrome with an additional command line argument:

chrome --allow-file-access-from-files main.html